Interface LinkedList

public interface LinkedList

This interface specifies the design for a doubly linked list storing double values. Most methods on this list are copied directly from the Java 6 List API. Feel free to read it if you have the time: http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/List.html
